    <item>
      <title>战争导致以色列经济增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/israel-s-economic-growth-revised-down-as-war-takes-heavy-toll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于与加沙哈马斯以及真主党持续不断的战争对经济造成的损失比之前预想的更为严重，以色列下调了第二季度的经济增速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/israel-s-economic-growth-revised-down-as-war-takes-heavy-toll</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 11:40:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印钞厂 De La Rue 因 3.92 亿美元的分拆计划而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/uk-money-printer-de-la-rue-soars-on-392-million-breakup-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德拉鲁 (De La Rue Plc) 同意将其印钞部门出售给 Crane NXT Co. 后，该公司股价出现四年多来的最大涨幅，从而导致这家拥有 200 多年历史的英国公司解体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/uk-money-printer-de-la-rue-soars-on-392-million-breakup-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 08:34:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
